Package: scResponse
Title: Response Scoring for Single-Cell RNA-seq Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
  c(
    person("Qi", "Dong", role = "aut"),
    person("Yuzheng", "Chen" , email = "yuzhengc46@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Tools for computing response-associated enrichment
    scores based on ranked gene expression in single-cell RNA-seq data.
    The package implements lightweight scoring and visualization
    functions without relying on large external frameworks.
